metadata.name: Perfects Love
metadata.description:
Perfects Love Club brings together soccer and volleyball and baseball and tennis and bowling and basketball and life and movement and the values of true uniqueness. Perfects Love PFPs is our dream to realize an iconic global game and launch a meta-universe drawn to get into a fairy tale with fabulous tasks and adventures, and we will, we already do. !

https://www.perfectslove.io
